## Types
  * type annotations: bounded quantification for constants , comments
  * qtt typevars + record fields
  * Dependent normalisation
  * Tuple
  * f x = _no_x is subtype of f = _
  * ensure pi binders are always lifted to the top level
  * ensure lambda args are counted in the domain of their parent function
  * Ensure dominion is working properly for let / lambda bindings
## CodeGen
  * GMP
  * conv recursive functions to anamorphisms (attempt to always avoid stacking)

